<section id="stack-apps" class="section">
  <div class="section-badge badge-red">Stack Applications</div>
  <h2>Stack Applications</h2>
  <p>Stacks are used everywhere — from evaluating math expressions to managing function calls and converting number bases.</p>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <div class="card" style="border-color:rgba(239,68,68,0.2)">
      <div class="card-icon">🔢</div>
      <h3>Decimal → Binary</h3>
      <p>Push remainders of successive divisions by 2. Pop all to get binary representation.</p>
