      <li>insertFront(x) — insert at front</li>
      <li>insertRear(x) — insert at rear</li>
      <li>deleteFront() — remove from front</li>
      <li>deleteRear() — remove from rear</li>
      <li>Use case: Sliding window problems, palindrome check, undo/redo</li>
